            pp 11-15. 
          </li><li>Wolfe, J. and Smith, J. (2008) &quot;<a href="reprints/WolfeSmithAA.pdf" target="_blank">Acoustical coupling between lip valves and vocal folds</a>&quot;, <i>Acoustics Australia</i>, <b>36</b>, 23-27.          
        </li></ul>
        <a href="didj_files.html" target="_blank">More sounds and videos</a><br />
